| ./folderstats/\_\_init\_\_.py | \_\_init\_\_      | py        | 2790  | 2018-12-23 23:09:07 | 2018-12-23 23:09:05 | 2018-12-23 23:09:05 | False  |           | 7b4adc532f304863423ec11afd3232ad | 
